Azerbaijan has played a major role in the achievement of Victory over fascism, the people of Azerbaijan have shown heroism during the war.
Speech to the Cabinet on the results of the Eurogroup. Watch at https://t.co/qJFwWaHW4q
Heydar Aliyev made exceptional services in the history of Azerbaijan, led the country from recession, from chaos to development, progress.
Today, Azerbaijan is a self-proclaimed state, a world that has been approved by the world and progresses with confidence.
The main goal of the policy pursued in Azerbaijan is to strengthen the independence. We are ready for all the challenges of the modern era.
The Eurogroup decision yesterday justifies our efforts and proves (1/2)
that Greece can do it without relinquishing unreasonable demands. (2/2)
We kept the agreement by keeping society upright.
At the heart of today's policy is the citizen of Azerbaijan, his problems, concerns and security.
At the same time, we have for the first time printed a roadmap for the Greek debt.
This creates a budgetary space for the recovery of the economy and the widening of social protection.
All the successes in Azerbaijan have been achieved only through the hard work of the people, as a result of well-thought-out policy.
Azerbaijan will continue to develop, and all the issues facing the country will be solved and will be solved.
I understand, of course, that the establishment has played its turn against the government. You see, hope dies last.
They tried to anticipate that we would be taking additional measures of € 3.6 billion. They almost wanted to accept.
Instead of seeing the forest, ie the closing of the assessment and the agreement on the Greek debt (1/2)
focus on the tree, the financial correction mechanism. (2/2)
Separatist tendencies in Nagorno-Karabakh were artificially provocative. And now Azerbaijan suffers the bitter consequences of this provocation
It is a mechanism that is already in place in Greece as well as in Europe.
This mechanism will not be implemented because for the first time in the 6 years of the crisis we have a soft adjustment program.
In April 2016, the Azerbaijani Army's Revolutionary Revolution triggered the power of the Azerbaijani state and Armed Forces, (cont) https://t.co/eQvlBwRngng
Now is not the time for celebrations. It is the time of work and the right planning.
To achieve a development that is not based on the crash of work and the unleashing of the oligarchy, but it will have a social sign.
The main task of Azerbaijan is to settle the Armenian-Azerbaijani Nagorno-Karabakh conflict on the basis of international law.
The orientation of all of us must turn to the great, real sections that the country and the Greek people need.
